  <h3 class="first"> OK, seriously.</h3>

  <h3 class="first">What is Flappy, the toy game controller?</h3>

  <br />
  <p class="first-p-wide">Flappy is a plush toy that controls the game on your phone or tablet. ‘The game’ is our version of the beloved ‘Flappy Bird’ by Dong Nguyen. To make Flappy fly in the game, you lift up Flappy (the toy)
  </p>

