<div class="wrapper" id="woah">
  <p class="first-p" id="space">
    <h3 class="first">
    Whoa, that’s cool! How does it work?
    </h3>

      <p class="first-p" id="space">
        Inside of Flappy is a sensor that connects wirelessly to your tablet or mobile device. The sensor detects motion, i.e. lifting Flappy up.
      </p>


      <div class="center" id="space">
        <%= image_tag 'flappy-iphone-ipad.png', size: "570x500" %>
      </div>

  <p class="first-p">Simply launch the game and bring Flappy near your device. Flappy connects automatically. Yep, kind of like magic. Now you’re ready to play!</p>


  <div class="center" id="space"></div>
  <div class="center" id="space"></div>
  <div class="center" id="space"></div>


